<article>
	<h1>Template Manager: Edit Source</h1>

	<p>This screen is accessed from the back-end administrator panel. It is used to edit the source code of template files.</p>
	<section>
		<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="How_to_Access">How to Access</span></h2>
		<p>Navigate to the <a href="<?php echo Route::url('index.php?option=com_help&view=help&keyref=Help25:Extensions_Template_Manager_Templates_Edit'); ?>" title="Help: Extensions Template Manager Templates Edit">Template Manager: Customise Template</a> screen. Click on the name of the template you want to edit. Then click the link to the template file that you want to edit.</p>
