		<p>At the top right you will see the toolbar. The functions are:</p>
		<ul>
			<li><b>Save</b>. Saves the template source file and stays in the current screen.</li>
			<li><b>Save &amp; Close</b>. Saves the template source file and closes the current screen.</li>
